text: Mehdi Zahedi (, born 5 December 1990) is an Iranian futsal player. He is currently a member of Hyper Shahr Shahin Shahr in the Iranian Futsal Super League. == Honours == === Club === * Iranian Futsal Hazfi Cup ** Champion (1): 2013–14 (Mahan Tandis Qom) == References == Category:1990 births Category:Living people Category:People from Qom Category:Iranian men's futsal players Category:Almas Shahr Qom FSC players Category:Arjan Shiraz FSC players
